 Future Scope
Backend Integration: Implementing Firebase or Node.js for persistent data storage and user authentication.

Payment Gateway: Full integration with Razorpay or Stripe for automated fee collection.

QR Check-in System: Generating unique QR codes on tickets for seamless offline event check-ins.

Automated Certificates: One-click certificate generation and distribution for participants.

In-App Messaging: Real-time chat for team collaboration and organizer-to-participant announcements.
